            <p class="mt-3 text-gray-500 dark:text-neutral-500">
            Transform your car's interior with our meticulous detailing service, ensuring every surface is cleaned and rejuvenated to perfection.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-auto flex border-t border-gray-200 divide-x divide-gray-200 dark:border-primary dark:divide-primary">
